twitch_info.title: Kamilia III - Shine & Bright Kill
twitch_info.description:
46.5 hours and 3,500 deaths. The most effort and stress I've ever gone through with a boss. Died on the final dice roll twice (5 and a 2 respectively), and avoidance was just hell.
Apologies for loud mic after the kill and unfortunately bitrate makes some attacks rough to see but it is what it is. So so happy to finally have downed it.
